|-------------------------------|--------------------|------------------|
|ICRC approval                  |6 months            |9-12 months       |
|State subsidiary agreement     |3 months            |6-9 months        |
|Hospital deployment            |2 months            |4-6 months        |
|International grant application|6 months            |12-18 months      |
|Pharma partnership             |6 months            |12-24 months      |

**Rule:** Add 50-100% to all theoretical timelines.

